*Zvaću* te u pet ujutro. (I will call you at five in the morning.)

*Zvao* sam ga pre nekog vremena. (I called him some time ago.)

*Zvat ću* je da se čujemo. (I will call her so that we can talk.)

*Zvao* bih je da se vidimo. (I would call her so that we can see each other.)

*Zvali* su nas da se pridružimo. (They called us to join them.)